---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Event Rounds - PSD">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Event Rounds</h1>
    <p>Information about event round structure and timing.</p>

    <div class="rounds-content">
      <section class="round-info">
        <h2>Round Structure</h2>
        <p>Our speed dating events consist of multiple timed rounds where participants rotate through partners.</p>
        
        <div class="round-cards">
          <div class="round-card">
            <h3>Round 1</h3>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> 5 minutes</p>
            <p>Meet your first partner and get to know each other</p>
          </div>

          <div class="round-card">
            <h3>Round 2</h3>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> 5 minutes</p>
            <p>Move to your next partner and repeat</p>
          </div>

          <div class="round-card">
            <h3>Round 3</h3>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> 5 minutes</p>
            <p>Continue meeting new people</p>
          </div>

          <div class="round-card">
            <h3>Round 4-5</h3>
            <p><strong>Duration:</strong> 5 minutes each</p>
            <p>Complete final rounds and take notes</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="breaks-info">
        <h2>Breaks Between Rounds</h2>
        <p>Between each round, there's a short break to catch your breath and take notes on your conversation.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Write down names and key details</li>
          <li>Indicate who you'd like to see again</li>
          <li>Prepare for next round</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="matching-info">
        <h2>After All Rounds</h2>
        <p>After completing all rounds, submit your preferences indicating which participants you'd like to connect with.</p>
        <p>We only share contact information when there's mutual interest!</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .rounds-content {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  .round-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .round-card {
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid #0066ff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .round-card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: #0066ff;
  }

  .round-card p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #666;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  ul li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: #666;
  }

  ul li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #27ae60;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
